begin_memory_text: We introduced ourselves and discussed where we live. Kobe told me that he lives in DC. We chatted about previous chats we had done through this study. I asked Kobe what it is like to live in DC during an election. This led into our discussion about politics
middle_memory_text: We talked about politics. Discussed Trump and how he needs to go. We talked about the SCOTUS nominee and how she is both a graduate and professor at my institution and clearly knows nothing about the constitution. We talked about the debates and the town halls.
end_memory_text: We talked about polls and if Biden was likely to win. Kobe thinks he will win and that its over at this point.

I have the weekend technically "off" from work but do usually do some work. There is less pressure on me if I don't do as much work as I plan to though, and I feel less guilt, so Im excited for the weekend.
critical_positive: It was very easy for us to continue the conversation without any gaps or awkward pauses. Kobe was a great conversation partner, and we had similar views on things, so it was easy for the conversation to take off.
